flowchart TD
    start[Kafka Transaction Received] --> sender{Sender ID exists?}
    sender -->|No| discard1[Discard transaction\nNo DB modification]
    sender -->|Yes| recipient{Recipient ID exists?}
    recipient -->|No| discard2[Discard transaction\nNo DB modification]
    recipient -->|Yes| funds{Sender balance >= amount?}
    funds -->|No| discard3[Discard transaction\nInsufficient funds]
    funds -->|Yes| valid[Valid transaction]
    valid --> incentive[Call Incentive API]
    incentive --> update[Update balances]
    update --> persist[Persist TransactionRecord]
